== 媒体中的使用 ==
苏联电影中，《工人和集体农庄女庄员》于1947年选中用作[[莫斯科电影制片厂|莫斯科电影制片厂]]的标志。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ytfiles.com/2009/12/10/worker-and-kolkhoz-woman-a-soviet-era-monument-finds-its-way-back-into-moscows-landscape/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-06-26 |archive-date=2009-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091231200746/http://www.ytfiles.com/2009/12/10/worker-and-kolkhoz-woman-a-soviet-era-monument-finds-its-way-back-into-moscows-landscape/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>可在电影《[[红色警探|红色警探]]》及其他由[[莫斯科电影制片厂|莫斯科电影制片厂]]自行出品的俄罗斯电影中的片头见到。

该雕像的大型活动复制品出现在了[[2014年冬季奥林匹克运动会|2014年索契冬奥会]][[2014年冬季奥林匹克运动会开幕式|开幕式]]上，<ref>{{cite news| title = Olympics Opening Ceremony Offers Fanfare for a Reinvented Russia| work = The New York Times| date = 7 February 2014| url = http://www.nytimes.com/2014/02/08/sports/olympics/russia-opens-sochi-games-with-pageantry-and-pride.html?_r=0| accessdate = 2009-02-09| archive-date = 2021-01-26| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210126072936/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/02/08/sports/olympics/russia-opens-sochi-games-with-pageantry-and-pride.html?_r=0| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| title = Sochi 2014 in five pictures| work = beranger.org| date = 7 February 2014| url = http://beranger.org/2014/02/07/sochi-2014-in-five-pictures/| accessdate = 2009-02-09| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://archive.is/20140209212605/http://beranger.org/2014/02/07/sochi-2014-in-five-pictures/| archivedate = 2014年2月9日}}</ref>象征[[布尔什维克革命|布尔什维克革命]]后的[[苏联五年计划|大规模工业化时期]]。

